교재 및 참고문헌: Although this course does not require students to have prior knowledge on governance and democracy, some students may want to get a general idea about major theories and perspectives pertaining to governance and democracy. The following books will help you acquire a basic familiarity on the topic. You don’t have to purchase them unless if you want. You can find all other required and recommended readings on electoral reserve:
>Jon Pierre (ed.). 2000. Debating Governance: Authority, Steering and Democracy (Oxford: Oxford University Press).
>David Levi-Faur (ed.). 2012/2014. Oxford Handbook of Governance (Oxford: Oxford University Press).
